1. Modify the Task class adding 'done' propetry which by default will be false
2. Add the method "markedAsDone() in the Task class wich sets true in 'done'

3. add method 'allDoneTasks()' in User class which returns an array  with only those tasks that have the proprety 'done' set as true;
4. add method 'allPendingTasks()' in User class which returns an array  only those tasks that have the proprety 'done' set as false;


5.add method 'unassignTasks(title)' in User class which will remove the task with this title